  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>Rail holidays in Europe</h2>
<p><span>Looking for a new way to see Europe? Put your holiday on the right track and step aboard a rail holiday to Europe. This is your ticket to the great outdoors, where you'll be treated to some of the most stunning views Europe has to offer. </span></p>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13095152/bernina_express_sommer.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="rail holidays europe" data-udi="umb://media/01a6e311c948429885f1b808c3255fb1" /></p>
<p>Departing from St Pancras, London, we offer unforgettable rail journeys to some of the most breath-taking destinations in <a data-udi="umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a>, as well as selected resorts in <a data-udi="umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf}" title="France">France</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy">Italy</a>. So if you're looking for a new kind of walking adventure that's off the beaten track, but still within reach of all the top sights and sounds then take a look at our rail holidays.</p>
<p> </p>
<h2>Our Rail holidays</h2>
<p>We've got your ticket to the most relaxing, luxurious travel experience in Europe. <span>Our rail holidays offer an exceptional European travel experience, all from the comfort of your train seat. Whether you crave the elegance of the <a data-udi="umb://document/d8a3be3fd1dd4a9393a346df4f3e910c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d8a3be3fd1dd4a9393a346df4f3e910c}" title="GoldenPass Line">Goldenpass Line</a> or the breath-taking views of the Swiss Alps on the <a data-udi="umb://document/ae29f8328e454cb08ae9ecf28f7078f4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae29f8328e454cb08ae9ecf28f7078f4}" title="Glacier Express">Glacier Express</a>, we have you covered.</span></p>
<p><strong>Call to book on: <span class="InfinityNumber">01483 319 625</span></strong></p>
<p> </p>
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Iconic rail journeys</h3>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/ae29f8328e454cb08ae9ecf28f7078f4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae29f8328e454cb08ae9ecf28f7078f4}" title="Glacier Express"><strong>The Glacier Express</strong></a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13095157/rail-holiday-1.jpg?width=500&amp;height=270" alt="rail holidays" data-udi="umb://media/2c21ccf1890c494baf6f5e115f9f5c6b" /></p>
<p><strong>Switzerland: </strong><strong>Interlaken<span> </span>– Zermatt – Davos/Klosters</strong></p>
<p><strong>10 or 11 nights</strong></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><span>If you love mountains, this is your train trip. Our 10 or 11 night independent rail holiday provides you with unforgettable views between <a data-udi="umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722}" title="Zermatt">Zermatt</a> and either </span><a data-udi="umb://document/527f062dda374fee961e7ca5209c3d26" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/switzerland/graubunden-region/davos" title="Davos">Davos</a><span> or </span><a data-udi="umb://document/5cdc3bd60ed74827b457178da3c4090e" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/switzerland/graubunden-region/klosters" title="Klosters">Klosters</a><span>. The specially designed panoramic carriages unlock superb views over the Swiss Alps.</span></span><a data-udi="umb://document/a9a7db62204445c9afab9589b4941af8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a9a7db62204445c9afab9589b4941af8}" title="Slovenia Savings"></a></p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/ae29f8328e454cb08ae9ecf28f7078f4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae29f8328e454cb08ae9ecf28f7078f4}" title="Glacier Express">Find out more</a></h3>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/d8a3be3fd1dd4a9393a346df4f3e910c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d8a3be3fd1dd4a9393a346df4f3e910c}" title="GoldenPass Line"><strong>Goldenpass Line</strong></a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13095158/swiss-rail-goldenpass.jpg?width=500&amp;height=270" alt="swiss rail holiday" data-udi="umb://media/0e2ec2eb61e14d7289b5bac85cbe8b1f" /></p>
<p><strong>Switzerland: </strong><strong>Montreux – Wengen – Lake Lucerne</strong></p>
<p><strong>10 or 11 nights</strong></p>
<p>Visit three very distinctive regions of<span> </span><a data-udi="umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/switzerland" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a><span> </span>on this three centre rail holiday which includes a trip on the<span> </span><a data-udi="umb://document/d8a3be3fd1dd4a9393a346df4f3e910c" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-switzerland/goldenpass-line" title="GoldenPass Line">GoldenPass line</a>. On your holiday you’ll have the opportunity to explore the Lavaux Vineyards, the mountainous Jungfrau area and the historical sites of <a data-udi="umb://document/56819e7662924ccf91baa56999b5cbef" href="/{localLink:umb://document/56819e7662924ccf91baa56999b5cbef}" title="Lucerne">Lucerne</a>. </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/d8a3be3fd1dd4a9393a346df4f3e910c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d8a3be3fd1dd4a9393a346df4f3e910c}" title="GoldenPass Line">Find out more</a></h3>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Multi-centre rail holidays</h3>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/d878f477114346f99e5f102f64f0e4e3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d878f477114346f99e5f102f64f0e4e3}" title="Venice, Florence &amp; Rome">Venice, Florence &amp; Rome</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13095206/italy-by-rail.jpg?width=500&amp;height=270" alt="italy rail holidays" data-udi="umb://media/41597763d1ea40d7b1d991e9a402ab2d" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Get a taste of Italy on this three-city tour from Venice to Rome. Visit galleries in Florence, wander along the Grand Canal in Venice and take in culture and history as you stroll through Rome's city centre. Take in the sights, sip on a rich espresso, and savour the finest wines on this unforgettable journey through the heart of Italy.</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></p>
<h3><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/d878f477114346f99e5f102f64f0e4e3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d878f477114346f99e5f102f64f0e4e3}" title="Venice, Florence &amp; Rome">Find out more</a></strong></h3>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/53a09958cf634d47abf56c4efd5c7912" href="/{localLink:umb://document/53a09958cf634d47abf56c4efd5c7912}" title="Rome &amp; Amalfi Coast">Rome &amp; Amalfi Coast</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13095205/rome-rail-holiday.jpg?width=500&amp;height=270" alt="rome rail holidays" data-udi="umb://media/1454e7f2e79040729a3e98c26161ced2" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Ready to savour the dolce vita? This exciting multi-centre holiday takes you to Italy's most iconic destinations: <a data-udi="umb://document/57bc5f34b7074843b7f19f3fc6cb7ac4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/57bc5f34b7074843b7f19f3fc6cb7ac4}" title="Rome">Rome</a> and the <a data-udi="umb://document/f13578bcd0ea422bb13fbbbc34693d47" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f13578bcd0ea422bb13fbbbc34693d47}" title="Amalfi Coast">Amalfi Coast</a>. From exploring charming coastal towns to experiencing ancient history at the Colosseum and the Vatican, this trip has it all.</span></p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/53a09958cf634d47abf56c4efd5c7912" href="/{localLink:umb://document/53a09958cf634d47abf56c4efd5c7912}" title="Rome &amp; Amalfi Coast">Find out more</a></h3>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/58868750b42d43d78a89df92df2b164f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/58868750b42d43d78a89df92df2b164f}" title="Swiss Classic Tour">Swiss Classic Tour</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13095156/swiss-rail-holiday.jpg?width=500&amp;height=270" alt="swiss classic tour" data-udi="umb://media/1b698dc01da042f0a44ff05ed99e67cd" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This 10-day multi-centre holiday will take you on a journey of a lifetime through Switzerland's breath-taking landscapes, giving you a true taste of this stunning country. Brace yourself for an unforgettable adventure aboard two of the most spectacular panoramic journeys in the world: the Bernia and <a data-udi="umb://document/ae29f8328e454cb08ae9ecf28f7078f4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae29f8328e454cb08ae9ecf28f7078f4}" title="Glacier Express">Glacier Express</a>.</span></p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/53a09958cf634d47abf56c4efd5c7912" href="/{localLink:umb://document/53a09958cf634d47abf56c4efd5c7912}" title="Rome &amp; Amalfi Coast">Find out more</a></h3>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2>Destinations you can reach by train from the UK</h2>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy">Italy</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13095203/italy-holidays.jpg?width=317&amp;height=171" alt="Italy by rail" data-udi="umb://media/82b0db05ab4f471189e4cbbf8447612e" /></p>
<p><span>London to Italy by train is easy with Eurostar to Paris and Voyages SNCF to Italy. Daytime services include trips to <a data-udi="umb://document/2575554a5b50446eb00d5bf533f317cd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2575554a5b50446eb00d5bf533f317cd}" title="Milan">Milan</a> or high-speed trains through the Swiss Alps to <a data-udi="umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a}" title="Lake Como">Lake Como</a> or <a data-udi="umb://document/476c8caf3fe84faab565f2d0f2e99f48" href="/{localLink:umb://document/476c8caf3fe84faab565f2d0f2e99f48}" title="Lake Maggiore">Lake Maggiore</a>. </span></p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy">View Italy holidays</a></h3>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13095200/switzerland.jpg?width=317&amp;height=171" alt="switzerland by rail" data-udi="umb://media/8c96ad88d99c40b2a16cbc2432d840fc" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><span>Take a scenic and comfortable journey to Switzerland by Eurostar from London to Paris, followed by a high-speed train to Geneva or Zurich with frequent direct connections to resorts.</span></span></p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d}" title="Switzerland">View Switzerland holidays</a></h3>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf}" title="France">France</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13095198/france-by-rail.jpg?width=317&amp;height=171" alt="France by rail" data-udi="umb://media/44766c70827144f0b37374572fc28f19" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Travel in style and arrive comfortably at your destination with high speed rail service from Paris to <a data-udi="umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/59d85c3607bf4fc5a291361000fe9db0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/59d85c3607bf4fc5a291361000fe9db0}" title="Lake Annecy">Annecy</a> and beyond. The fastest trains from Paris to Chamonix take around 5 hours and 30 minutes, covering a distance of approximately 473 kilometres.</span></p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf}" title="France">View France holidays</a></h3>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Step into summer with Inghams</strong></h2>
<p><strong><img src="/media/13089493/our-holidays-838x220.jpg" alt="Step into Summer" data-udi="umb://media/b40cf9d23b4a4012aaed9b15dfdb0eab" /></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">✔️ With over 85 years of experience you can trust us to deliver your perfect holiday.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">✔️ You'll have the reassurance and expert guidance of our reps when in resort.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">✔️ <strong>New for 2023:</strong> enjoy two guided walks per week in selected resorts*.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">✔️Flights from your choice of 15 regional airports, transfers and accommodation are included in your holiday.</p>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2>Travel With Confidence</h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">When you choose an Inghams holiday, you can travel with confidence. We’re here to take the stress out of travelling. We’ve put extra measures in place for your peace of mind. We’ll help keep both you and your money safe.</span></p>
<p><img style="width: 0px; height: 0px;" src="/media/13090673/in-safe-hands-flexibility-838x330-may-22.jpg?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/46fe0fd3483443e6ae1e1a418008a220" /><a data-udi="umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae}" title="In Safe Hands"><img src="/media/13090673/in-safe-hands-flexibility-838x330-may-22.jpg" alt="In Safe Hands Inghams" data-udi="umb://media/46fe0fd3483443e6ae1e1a418008a220" /></a></p>
<p><strong>Terms and Conditions</strong></p>
<p>**<span>Up to two guided walks per week are included in the following resorts: </span><a data-udi="umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/austria/austrian-tyrol/mayrhofen" title="Mayrhofen">Mayrhofen</a><span>, <a data-udi="umb://document/a71713291d5d4220aea1b806f34cd053" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a71713291d5d4220aea1b806f34cd053}" title="Seefeld">Seefeld</a>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/ab49d5977a794ec7952da3e3d5adf48b" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/austria/saalbach-hinterglemm" title="Saalbach &amp; Hinterglemm">Saalbach &amp; Hinterglemm</a><span>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/france/chamonix" title="Chamonix">Chamonix</a><span>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/a95b5199e8e04283bf8eeeabb42715fc" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/france/morzine" title="Morzine">Morzine</a><span>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/604dbba59ac64320ab6e9f1e89231a4c" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/limone" title="Limone">Limone</a><span>, <a data-udi="umb://document/c5c478381e04431da3f69d8364215ae7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c5c478381e04431da3f69d8364215ae7}" title="Merano">Merano</a>,<a data-udi="umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd}" title="Selva"> Selva</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/b45a359445114107972cbb2b00be85ae" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b45a359445114107972cbb2b00be85ae}" title="Champoluc" data-anchor="#">Champoluc</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/de185d9ae756482295e4f069ba3a7aaf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/de185d9ae756482295e4f069ba3a7aaf}" title="Cervinia">Cervinia</a>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/slovenia/kranjska-gora" title="Kranjska Gora">Kranjska Gora</a><span>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/switzerland/bernese-oberland/grindelwald" title="Grindelwald">Grindelwald</a><span>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/dd4c4793225641fcb24c0918a33714b3" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/switzerland/bernese-oberland/wengen" title="Wengen">Wengen</a><span> and </span><a data-udi="umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/switzerland/zermatt" title="Zermatt">Zermatt</a><span>. </span><span>All walks are subject to availability of local guides, weather conditions and maximum numbers. Where we cannot confirm your preferred option in resort, we will endeavour to offer an alternative subject to the above conditions. </span></p>]]></bodyText>
